original: You hunch down and walk as fast as you dare. You keep near walls and stay well away from what you think are roads. You hope no one sees you in such a humiliating predicament, but at the same time you know you need help.
You hunch down beside a wall in what you hope is a sheltered position.
You feel soil beneath your feet and hear <<if Time.hour gte 7 and Time.hour lte 20>>the distant sounds of the town.<<else>>a wolf howling disturbingly close.<</if>>
The tattered blindfold falls to pieces around your head, freeing you. You squint against the light.
